  General methodology: The global approach considered in this     6329 1451   66
          work is presented in the following paper: Modern        6329 1451   67
          nuclear data evaluation with the TALYS code system,     6329 1451   68
          A.J. Koning and D. Rochman, Nuclear Data Sheets 113     6329 1451   69
          (2012) 2841.                                            6329 1451   70
